Gallery 1.4.0

	* [Bug] Fixed some of the exif data, (if the image has exif data, but it's blank).
	* [Feature] Added support for videos, music, and any arbitrary file.
	* [Feature] Added integration with jPlayer to provide an inline video player.
	* [Feature] Added sm, med, and lg options for individual photo previews.
	* [Feature] Added multisite support.
	* Set the gallery listing page to respect access permissions.
	* Radically redisigned the main view page to make more use of jquery masonry.
	-- Charlie Powell <charlie@eval.bz>  30 Dec 2012

